snippet.title: End Of An Era | Calamity Infernum Mod Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Engineer and the Witch, your final, fated opponents.
After over 2 years of development, it's all coming to an, explosive, end. Thanks for sticking around.

World Download for the arenas shown in this trailer:
https://mega.nz/folder/qhxUkRiT#wwXiiaZe_3EOk6nR50r8UQ

Infernum Mod Discord Server:
https://discord.gg/cKh6nyrSE7

What is the Infernum mod?
Infernum mod is an extension mod for Calamity that adds an extra difficulty - "Infernum", that's harder than Death mode, with a primary focus on expansive reworking of boss AIs.

My Discord Server:
https://discord.gg/mhgzw3qyeb
